* Sakari Pietilä, ice hockey player
* Lasse Pirjetä, ice hockey player
* Samuli Pohjamo, Member of the European Parliament
* Jukka Poika, singer
* Jukka Rasila, actor
* Riitta-Liisa Roponen, cross-country skier
