<doc id="774391" wikidata="Q1641672" url="?curid=774391" title="Joroinen">
<text>Joroinen is a municipality in the North Savo region of Finland. It is located in the province of Eastern Finland and is part of the Northern Savonia sub-region. The municipality has a population of approximately 4,626 people and covers an area of 982 square kilometers.

