<doc id="774393" wikidata="Q127808" url="?curid=774393" title="Questembert">
<text>Questembert (; ) is a commune in the Morbihan department in Brittany in north-western France.

It is located approximately from Vannes.

==Demographics==
Inhabitants of Questembert are called &quot;Questembertois&quot;. Its population was 7,723 as of 2018.

==Breton language==

In 2008, 3.61% of local children attended bilingual schools in primary education, learning partly in Breton.

