* Wesley Livsey Jones, United States senator and congressman from the state of Washington
* Wesley N. Jones, American politician in North Carolina
* Wes Jones, American architect, educator and author</text><links>
<link wikidata="Q2563987" start="29" end="48" title="Wesley Livsey Jones" label="Wesley Livsey Jones"/>
<link wikidata="Q97585961" start="119" end="134" title="Wesley N. Jones" label="Wesley N. Jones"/>
