* Guide to the Harry Pratt Judson Papers 1889-1901 at the University of Chicago Special Collections Research Center
*Guide to the University of Chicago Office of the President, Harper, Judson and Burton Administrations Records 1869-1925 at the University of Chicago Special Collections Research Center</text><links>
